{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So I'm here to explain"},{"time":2000,"text":"why I'm wearing these ninja pajamas."},{"time":4000,"text":"And to do that, I'd like to talk first"},{"time":6000,"text":"about environmental toxins in our bodies."},{"time":9000,"text":"So some of you may know"},{"time":11000,"text":"about the chemical Bisphenol A, BPA."},{"time":13000,"text":"It's a material hardener and synthetic estrogen"},{"time":16000,"text":"that's found in the lining of canned foods"},{"time":18000,"text":"and some plastics."},{"time":20000,"text":"So BPA mimics the body's own hormones"},{"time":23000,"text":"and causes neurological and reproductive problems."},{"time":26000,"text":"And it's everywhere."},{"time":28000,"text":"A recent study found BPA"},{"time":30000,"text":"in 93 percent of people six and older."},{"time":34000,"text":"But it's just one chemical."},{"time":36000,"text":"The Center for Disease Control in the U.S."},{"time":39000,"text":"says we have 219 toxic pollutants in our bodies,"},{"time":43000,"text":"and this includes preservatives, pesticides"},{"time":46000,"text":"and heavy metals like lead and mercury."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49000,"text":"To me, this says three things."},{"time":51000,"text":"First, don't become a cannibal."},{"time":55000,"text":"Second, we are both responsible for and the victims of"},{"time":58000,"text":"our own pollution."},{"time":60000,"text":"And third,"},{"time":62000,"text":"our bodies are filters and storehouses"},{"time":64000,"text":"for environmental toxins."},{"time":67000,"text":"So what happens to all these toxins when we die?"},{"time":70000,"text":"The short answer is:"},{"time":72000,"text":"They return to the environment in one way or another,"},{"time":74000,"text":"continuing the cycle of toxicity."},{"time":76000,"text":"But our current funeral practices"},{"time":78000,"text":"make the situation much worse."},{"time":80000,"text":"If you're cremated,"},{"time":82000,"text":"all those toxins I mentioned are released into the atmosphere."},{"time":85000,"text":"And this includes 5,000 pounds of mercury"},{"time":88000,"text":"from our dental fillings alone every year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91000,"text":"And in a traditional American funeral,"},{"time":94000,"text":"a dead body is covered with fillers and cosmetics"},{"time":97000,"text":"to make it look alive."},{"time":99000,"text":"It's then pumped with toxic formaldehyde"},{"time":102000,"text":"to slow decomposition --"},{"time":104000,"text":"a practice which causes respiratory problems and cancer"},{"time":107000,"text":"in funeral personnel."},{"time":110000,"text":"So by trying to preserve our dead bodies,"},{"time":113000,"text":"we deny death, poison the living"},{"time":116000,"text":"and further harm the environment."},{"time":118000,"text":"Green or natural burials, which don't use embalming,"},{"time":121000,"text":"are a step in the right direction,"},{"time":123000,"text":"but they don't address the existing toxins in our bodies."},{"time":127000,"text":"I think there's a better solution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129000,"text":"I'm an artist,"},{"time":131000,"text":"so I'd like to offer a modest proposal"},{"time":133000,"text":"at the intersection"},{"time":135000,"text":"of art, science and culture."},{"time":137000,"text":"The Infinity Burial Project,"},{"time":139000,"text":"an alternative burial system"},{"time":141000,"text":"that uses mushrooms"},{"time":143000,"text":"to decompose and clean toxins in bodies."},{"time":145000,"text":"The Infinity Burial Project"},{"time":147000,"text":"began a few years ago with a fantasy"},{"time":149000,"text":"to create the Infinity Mushroom --"},{"time":151000,"text":"a new hybrid mushroom"},{"time":153000,"text":"that would decompose bodies, clean the toxins"},{"time":156000,"text":"and deliver nutrients to plant roots,"},{"time":158000,"text":"leaving clean compost."},{"time":160000,"text":"But I learned it's nearly impossible"},{"time":162000,"text":"to create a new hybrid mushroom."},{"time":164000,"text":"I also learned"},{"time":166000,"text":"that some of our tastiest mushrooms"},{"time":168000,"text":"can clean environmental toxins in soil."},{"time":170000,"text":"So I thought maybe I could train an army"},{"time":173000,"text":"of toxin-cleaning edible mushrooms"},{"time":176000,"text":"to eat my body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178000,"text":"So today, I'm collecting what I shed or slough off --"},{"time":181000,"text":"my hair, skin and nails --"},{"time":184000,"text":"and I'm feeding these to edible mushrooms."},{"time":187000,"text":"As the mushrooms grow,"},{"time":189000,"text":"I pick the best feeders"},{"time":191000,"text":"to become Infinity Mushrooms."},{"time":193000,"text":"It's a kind of imprinting and selective breeding process"},{"time":196000,"text":"for the afterlife."},{"time":198000,"text":"So when I die,"},{"time":200000,"text":"the Infinity Mushrooms will recognize my body"},{"time":202000,"text":"and be able to eat it."},{"time":204000,"text":"All right, so for some of you,"},{"time":206000,"text":"this may be really, really out there."},{"time":208000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":210000,"text":"Just a little."}]},{"cues":[{"time":212000,"text":"I realize this is not the kind of relationship"},{"time":215000,"text":"that we usually aspire to have with our food."},{"time":218000,"text":"We want to eat, not be eaten by, our food."},{"time":221000,"text":"But as I watch the mushrooms grow"},{"time":223000,"text":"and digest my body,"},{"time":225000,"text":"I imagine the Infinity Mushroom"},{"time":227000,"text":"as a symbol of a new way of thinking about death"},{"time":230000,"text":"and the relationship between my body and the environment."},{"time":233000,"text":"See for me,"},{"time":235000,"text":"cultivating the Infinity Mushroom"},{"time":237000,"text":"is more than just scientific experimentation"},{"time":239000,"text":"or gardening or raising a pet,"},{"time":242000,"text":"it's a step towards accepting the fact"},{"time":244000,"text":"that someday I will die and decay."},{"time":247000,"text":"It's also a step"},{"time":249000,"text":"towards taking responsibility"},{"time":251000,"text":"for my own burden on the planet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":254000,"text":"Growing a mushroom is also part of a larger practice"},{"time":256000,"text":"of cultivating decomposing organisms"},{"time":258000,"text":"called decompiculture,"},{"time":260000,"text":"a concept that was developed by an entomologist,"},{"time":263000,"text":"Timothy Myles."},{"time":265000,"text":"The Infinity Mushroom is a subset of decompiculture"},{"time":268000,"text":"I'm calling body decompiculture and toxin remediation --"},{"time":272000,"text":"the cultivation of organisms that decompose"},{"time":274000,"text":"and clean toxins in bodies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277000,"text":"And now about these ninja pajamas."},{"time":279000,"text":"Once it's completed,"},{"time":281000,"text":"I plan to integrate the Infinity Mushrooms into a number of objects."},{"time":284000,"text":"First, a burial suit"},{"time":286000,"text":"infused with mushroom spores,"},{"time":288000,"text":"the Mushroom Death Suit."},{"time":290000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":292000,"text":"I'm wearing the second prototype"},{"time":294000,"text":"of this burial suit."},{"time":296000,"text":"It's covered with a crocheted netting"},{"time":299000,"text":"that is embedded with mushroom spores."},{"time":301000,"text":"The dendritic pattern you see"},{"time":303000,"text":"mimics the growth of mushroom mycelia,"},{"time":306000,"text":"which are the equivalent of plant roots."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308000,"text":"I'm also making a decompiculture kit,"},{"time":310000,"text":"a cocktail of capsules"},{"time":312000,"text":"that contain Infinity Mushroom spores"},{"time":314000,"text":"and other elements"},{"time":316000,"text":"that speed decomposition and toxin remediation."},{"time":319000,"text":"These capsules are embedded in a nutrient-rich jelly,"},{"time":322000,"text":"a kind of second skin,"},{"time":324000,"text":"which dissolves quickly"},{"time":326000,"text":"and becomes baby food for the growing mushrooms."},{"time":329000,"text":"So I plan to finish the mushroom and decompiculture kit"},{"time":332000,"text":"in the next year or two,"},{"time":334000,"text":"and then I'd like to begin testing them,"},{"time":337000,"text":"first with expired meat from the market"},{"time":339000,"text":"and then with human subjects."},{"time":341000,"text":"And believe it or not,"},{"time":343000,"text":"a few people have offered to donate their bodies to the project"},{"time":346000,"text":"to be eaten by mushrooms."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":352000,"text":"What I've learned from talking to these folks"},{"time":354000,"text":"is that we share a common desire"},{"time":356000,"text":"to understand and accept death"},{"time":359000,"text":"and to minimize the impact of our death on the environment."},{"time":362000,"text":"I wanted to cultivate this perspective"},{"time":365000,"text":"just like the mushrooms,"},{"time":367000,"text":"so I formed the Decompiculture Society,"},{"time":369000,"text":"a group of people called decompinauts"},{"time":372000,"text":"who actively explore their postmortem options,"},{"time":375000,"text":"seek death acceptance"},{"time":377000,"text":"and cultivate decomposing organisms"},{"time":379000,"text":"like the Infinity Mushroom."},{"time":382000,"text":"The Decompiculture Society shares a vision"},{"time":384000,"text":"of a cultural shift,"},{"time":386000,"text":"from our current culture of death denial and body preservation"},{"time":389000,"text":"to one of decompiculture,"},{"time":391000,"text":"a radical acceptance of death and decomposition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":395000,"text":"Accepting death means accepting"},{"time":397000,"text":"that we are physical beings"},{"time":399000,"text":"who are intimately connected to the environment,"},{"time":401000,"text":"as the research on environmental toxins confirms."},{"time":404000,"text":"And the saying goes,"},{"time":406000,"text":"we came from dust and will return to dust."},{"time":409000,"text":"And once we understand that we're connected to the environment,"},{"time":412000,"text":"we see that the survival of our species"},{"time":414000,"text":"depends on the survival of the planet."},{"time":416000,"text":"I believe this is the beginning"},{"time":419000,"text":"of true environmental responsibility."}]},{"cues":[{"time":421000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}